            . I live with Wm. Jones, a pawnbroker. These handkerchiefs were safe in his shop on the afternoon of the 20th of August - I did not miss them till they were brought to me next morning - I know nothing of the prisoners.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18270913-268-person2165">
                  BENJAMIN 
                  TIMBRELL
               <interp inst="t18270913-268-person2165" type="surname" value="TIMBRELL"></interp>
