                     <interp inst="t18270913-268-person2165" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am an officer. I received information, and took the prisoners, in company together, between nine and ten o'clock in the morning of the 21st of August; I found on Gallighan these six handkerchiefs, between his shirt and waistcoat.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18270913-268-person2166">
                  WILLIAM 
                  SCHOFIELD
               <interp inst="t18270913-268-person2166" type="surname" value="SCHOFIELD"></interp>
