                     <interp inst="t18270913-268-person2166" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I was with Timbrell. I found these eleven handkerchiefs on Moody.(Property produced and sworn to.)</p>
               <p>MOODY's Defence. I was near the Horse Guards, and met a man running very fast with two or three bundles - he dropped one, which I took up; it contained this property.</p>
               <p>GALLIGHAN's Defence. I met my fellow prisoner - a man in a blue cloak ran by us; he dropped a bundle - we took it up, and shared the handkerchiefs.</p>
